    "description": "<p>SiS Technologies Pte Ltd is a wholly owned subsidiary of &nbsp;SiS International Holdings Ltd,<br>\na company listed on the Main Board of The Stock Exchange of Hong Kong Limited<br>\n(Stock code: 0529). SiS Technologies was first founded in 1983 and rapidly became<br>\none of the largest distributors of IT products in Singapore and across other Asian<br>\ncountries.<br>\n <br>\nAs a value-added distributor, SiS Technologies not only provides a wide variety of IT<br>\nproducts, but also offers comprehensive IT Consulting Services. We take pride in<br>\ndelivering business solutions through our partners to our customers, thus contributing to<br>\nthe proliferate success of their businesses. <br>\n <br>\nOur success relies on our passionate and visionary management team. Amongst the<br>\ndistribution arena in Singapore, SiS Technologies stands out as being deeply focused<br>\non SiS Technologies stands out with its deep focus on cybersecurity, cloud, networking,<br>\ninfrastructure, collaborations and AI technologies. Belted with over 30 years of experience<br>\nand our deep knowledge of evolving IT landscape, complemented with our established<br>\nreputation and exceptional personnel, we are confident in representing and delivering<br>\nany worldwide products and IT solutions.</p>",
